flowRoot.flowPara: Majority of login times occur during normal business hours 8 am – 4:59 pm. The most logins occur in the 9 am hour, but there appear to be 2 “waves” of logins centered around the 9 am hour and the 2 pm hour.
Login attempts occur most frequently on Monday and then a downward trend occurs for the rest of the week. Very little weekend activity comparatively.
